==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[finis]]'' end + ''-alis'' -al

===Noun===
'''final'''

# The ending, the last.
# A playoff round consisting of only two teams left.
# A [[test]] or [[examination]] given at the end of a [[term]] or [[class]]; the test that concludes a class.

